3 ways of compressing and uncompressing
$ bzip2 test.img           //compress            $ bunzip2 test.img.bz2           //uncompress
$ du -sh test.img.bz2      //verify              $ du -sh test.img                //verify

$ gzip test.img            //compress            $ gunzip test.img.gz             //uncompress     
$ du -sh test.img.gz       //verify              $ du -sh test.img                //verify

$ xz test.img              //compress            $ unxz test.img.xz               //uncompress
$ du -sh test.img.xz       //verify              $ du -sh test.img                //verify

read a compressed file without uncompressing it: zcat/bzcat/xzcat
$ zcat test.txt.bz2


